additional_info:
keywords: url address remove hide border separator slim thin revert return previous undo old padding margin whitespace white space button toolbar toolbarbutton

<b>Bonus</b>:

Insert this code into the style to remove a few more pixels of whitespace near the toolbarbutton area.

<pre>#urlbar .textbox-input-box.urlbar-input-box {
margin-right: 0 !important;
}</pre>

css:
@namespace url(http://www.mozilla.org/keymaster/gatekeeper/there.is.only.xul);
@-moz-document url(chrome://browser/content/browser.xul) {

#urlbar > toolbarbutton {
padding: 0 4px 0 2px !important;
margin-left: 0 !important;
border: none !important;
}

}
